{"tid":2238023,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄒家成: 警方拘捕行動只會更加深群眾對警方有預謀、串通內地「賣豬仔」的懷疑","createTime":"2020-10-10T18:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T02:24:03.000Z","uid":240362,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3a1fdb7cb87b50cc721d951ec6ed5df69f334511","tid":2238023,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T18:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9HLOWZdAl3_Wu7uopUEoMwtiGmI=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FYBLGKQBDFE5ZJNKYNNUNCZCTE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9HLOWZdAl3_Wu7uopUEoMwtiGmI%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFYBLGKQBDFE5ZJNKYNNUNCZCTE.jpg&h=c398c011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方以「協助逃犯」之名拘捕九人，指他們涉嫌協助12港人逃走，12港人家屬發表聲明，批評警方行動是試圖轉移視線，更表明一定會追究港警與中共勾結將12人送中的始末和責任。協助12港人家屬的鄒家成代表家屬指，警方行動加深群眾對警方有預謀、串通內地「賣豬仔」的懷疑。<br />\n<br />\n12港人家屬指，儘管面對越來越大的政治壓力，他們絕不放棄爭取家人早日回港，並會盡力查明真相。<br />\n<br />\n鄒家成代表家屬指，警方拘捕行動只會更加深群眾對警方有預謀、串通內地「賣豬仔」的懷疑，難以令公眾心服口服，同時令港府無法挽回民心，除非警方重視家屬要求，盡快交出事發時的雷達紀錄，或者催促內地讓12人返港，讓真相水落石出。他指，家屬們再次要求當局查明真相，並警告港府和警方勿混淆視聽。<br />\n<br />\n鄒表示，有家屬特別指出，警方「拒絕承認錯失、大話冚大話」的行為對家屬造成極大傷害，並更借用警方昨日的說法，斥責拘捕行動會令警方更抬不起頭做人，同時使到關心警方的人受到極大傷害、失望和負擔。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201011/K5REMHNHANBN5EBP4BXUBC6THM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201011%2FK5REMHNHANBN5EBP4BXUBC6THM%2F&d=bDSN5K49m9pAVz54ArwUlb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=6a4d9f92\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201011%2FK5REMHNHANBN5EBP4BXUBC6THM%2F&h=92bff2af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201011/K5REMHNHANBN5EBP4BXUBC6THM/</a>"},{"pid":"196c0b40d7470ca8e31d2f6c97ce20c84bc853bd","tid":2238023,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T18:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eacabb4d04a6fc01c8bca419968da30182f1b21","tid":2238023,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T18:22:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cccedff567c49f0879088fad3e45493a2ec23e49","tid":2238023,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T18:23:34.000Z","msg":"根本一早知 唔係邊有咁快拉到後面班幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90e899c43cb8c06bf1f909d0d5a7fb6428e487b0","tid":2238023,"uid":156863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T18:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd987a2a221fd109b428a53165b09c3a0d0b077f","tid":2238023,"uid":103965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T18:24:11.000Z","msg":"屌真係230先出消 智障"},{"pid":"7851824a23035184f258322c1a7eac440e32e17e","tid":2238023,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"196c0b40d7470ca8e31d2f6c97ce20c84bc853bd","tid":2238023,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T18:22:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"